---
title: Easy Chicken, Asparagus & Silverbeet Risotto with Parmesan
description: Get super cosy with the ultimate comfort dish. With tender chicken, punchy garlic paste and Parmesan, we're betting you'll be in
love with this risotto way before the last bite.
